Introduction

Gaeun is a South Korean dancer and singer.

She is a former member of the pre-debut sub unit LIMELIGHT, from which she was revealed as a member on August 12, 2022, and released the pre-debut EP "Limelight" on September 29, 2022, before making her official debut with them on February 17, 2023, with the EP "Love & Happiness".

On July 15, 2024, LIMELIGHT rebranded as MADEIN, and, on July 29, all seven members were officially announced. The group debuted on September 3, 2024, with their first EP "Rise".

On November 11, 2024, it was stated by the agency that Gaeun would be on hiatus for some time due to health reasons.

A few days later, on November 22, JTBC's Crime Chief reported that a rookie girl group member has been victim of SA and harassment by her company's CEO, with the rumors of it being Gaeun and 143 Entertainment's CEO respectively. On the same day, 143 Entertainment refuted the claims of SA while also confirming that the CEO had made sexual advancements with Gaeun.

On November 29, 2024, Gaeun's departure of MADEIN was announced, with the reason for it being personal circumstances.
